metadata.name: STEEL BRIDGE
metadata.description: THIS IS A 350-TON VEHICULAR BRIDGE THAT REALLY EXISTS IN COLOMBIA, WE MANUFACTURED IT IN MY COMPANY, AND I WANTED TO MAKE IT NFT, BECAUSE A BRIDGE IS A SYMBOL OF UNION, CURRENTLY THIS BRIDGE LINKS TWO FAR-FROM CITIES IN MY COUNTRY AND WE DID IT WITH THE HELP OF MANY VULNERABLE SITUATION PEOPLE
